text:
Pehle din se pata nahi kaise bade bhaiya wale vibes deta aa rha hai. Jaate jaate bhi bade bhaiya jaise gaya. Volleyball khelne mein maza to tere saath hi aata tha, aur khelna chahiye tha tereko xD. As always, Respect 100.
P.S. Mast bio hai yrr :)
author: Prajjwal  Mishra

text: Apne wing ka mechanic aur rich boy – Chinglee wala Archit. Tere dubbe mein ek do baar kya khel liya, lifelong gaming addict ban gaya. Tera initiative kaafi inspiring rha hai. Jab bhi koi idea aata, koi saath de na de – tu to kar ke hi chhodta, chahe akele hi kyon na ho. Waiting for the day jab tereko pyjama/shorts/chappal mein dekhunga lol.
author: Prajjwal  Mishra

text: Yo Sachin Arya! Tera overall attitude bohot hi pyara tha and that’s why teri subtly lene mein itna maza aata tha (also why tu wing ka ‘hagga’ ban baitha). Tere aur cc ke debates miss karoonga (ande vs non veg lmao). Wing mein sabse zaada khelna ka enthu tere mein hi rheta tha, aur khelte khelte pata nahi kahan se kahan pohonch gaya. Discord pe aa jaya kar bsdk.

text: Kya yaar, I’ll really miss the friend jiske room pe mein jab mann kare, aur kitni hi trivial baat ho, rr karne aa jaata. Waise to tereko cse mein branch change karna tha magar ab jo physics mein ghus hi gaya hai to nobel leke hi nikalna. Jab prof banega to harami mat ban jaana. Tere room pe khoob maze kiye hai, hopefully future mein bhi karne ko milega.

text: Bhai wo sandwitches kya gazab addictive the. Dubara khaane tonk tak aa jaunga, bas wo restaurant khulte hi message drop kar dena. Waiting for the day jab tu CC ki TT mein gaand maar dega. Keep reading.
author: Prajjwal  Mishra

text: Wing’s stereotypical ‘Jaat’ and apne football aur volleyball teams ka core (aur founding) player – tu bohot pyara aur seedha insaan hai. Jo andar wo bahar, hamesha dil ki baat bolta hai; cc, kajala jaise log chahe jitna bhi chidhaein. Will always remember fever ke time pe tune kitni help ki thi. Hamesha aise hi chhaati phula ke chalte rehna xD.
author: Prajjwal  Mishra

text: Wing goalkeeper, human calculator, human atlas and a go to point for campus rumours, random info/stats and recommendations ranging from courses to tv series. With your no-fucks-given wala attitude, no pretence at morality and absolutely zero confusion/randi rona, tu literally only banda hai jisse I’ll think twice before starting an argument, but these same things make you the most reliable of friends in times of need. Kya be, corona nahi hota to khoob maze kiye hote (though not complaining about arknights lol), koi nahi, future mein to milte hi rahenge.
author: Prajjwal  Mishra

text: Kisi ki lete wakt tere chhehere pe jo raunak aati thi hamesha yaad rahegi lol, Day 1 mein khudko y16 keheke ek sg ki le rha tha, aakhri din tak malfoy-malfoy karta rha. Beech mein apne ‘bete’ ki lene ke liye football fan tak ban gaya. Ek saal pehle tak kya gol-gol sa tha, ek saal baad dekhunga to pata nahi shayad six pack leke ghoom rha ho :)
author: Prajjwal  Mishra

text: Despite first impressions, tu actually kaafi sahi banda nikla. Ofc tu bhi in 4 saalo mein kaafi improve kiya hai, even tera code bhi readable levels pe aa gaya hai – though abhi bhi there are times jab tu operators ke dono taraf space nahi deta smh. Kabhi actually srajit ke saath ghoome jaata hai to mein khud aa jaunga, ghaseetne ki zarurat nahi hogi :). Agar kabhi quantum computers chal gae to Q. Secure cryptosystems vale startup mein pakka involve karna.
author: Prajjwal  Mishra

text: Hall ka sabse lovable saanp :) Bohot hi seedha sa launda hai – aise hi rhe. Hyd mein to milte rhenge.
author: Prajjwal  Mishra

text:
Memoir sochte hi sabse pehle ek cheez hi dimag mein aati hai lol. Bc saath mein kya kya nahi discuss kiya hai. From talking roman history to debating mmorpgs vs gacha to HxH chimera ant arc. From analyzing witcher 3 choices to criticizing novels to making an anime storyline of a betrayal run (btw still waiting to see you, as a traitor with might 8, make a might roll of 3+ xD). Add to that all the assignments, football, cbg and everything else I can’t remember. IITK was so much more fun thanks to you.
PS. Thanks for the vim lessons, but I think I’ll stick with vs code :)
author: Prajjwal  Mishra

text: Wing ka best (and only) camera-man and story teller. Tere memories wale obsession ke wajah se aaj itne mast videos hai apne paas. Assignments mein tu aur Batra were legit the best group I could ask for (bas har course mein agle sem ka threat deke tere fraudyness ko counter nahi karna hota to better hota lol). Mere room pe (against my will) full volume hindi gaane chalaane ke liye thanks, due to that I found a few that weren’t totally low iq. Not to mention tera jo diwaar pe running commentry chalta tha (“surely you aren’t joking mr draap” lmao). Job shuru hone ke baad bhool mat jaio.
author: Prajjwal  Mishra

text: Enjoyer of all good things, except cbg. Tere saath kaafi recommendations exchange kiye hai, zaada rr bhi nahi karta aur khud kaafi bakchod cheeze suggest karta – even if you never completed some games yourself :(. Tereko dekh dekh mein bhi reddit addict ban gaya. Last ke kuch mahine (jab hafte mein 5 din ghar pe nhi hota) kaafi maze kiye tere room pe. Future mein pakka milte rhena hai.
author: Prajjwal  Mishra

text: Literally the definition of consistency – chahe cpi ho ya football mein support (btw tereko dekhke mereko bhi khoob mann karta tha ki Chelsea jeete). Aage bhi consistent rehna, kabhi aisa na ho ki koi random semis ke chakkar mein quiz chhoot jae lol.
author: Prajjwal  Mishra
